    <br>
    <span>1. implore (verb):</span> beg someone earnestly or desperately to do something.
    <br>
    &#10140; I regretfully and respectfully implore you to help us.
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <span>2. despair (noun):</span> the complete loss or absence of hop
    <br>
